      "value": {
        "latex": "Non commutative, associative, $(1,0)$ = {\\'e}lt neutre,\\par\n               $(a,b)$ est r{\\'e}gulier $\\iff a \\ne 0$. \\par\n               $(a,b)$ est inversible $\\iff a = \\pm1$.",
        "html": "<p>Non commutative, associative, <span class=\"math inline\">\\((1,0)\\)</span> = <span>é</span>lt neutre,</p>\n<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\((a,b)\\)</span> est r<span>é</span>gulier <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\iff a \\ne 0\\)</span>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\((a,b)\\)</span> est inversible <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\iff a = \\pm1\\)</span>.</p>\n"
